                            <p class="text-muted small">ORDERS DELIVERED<br />SUCCESSFUL EVERYDAY</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <h3 class="display-6 fw-bold">725+</h3>
                            <p class="text-muted small">STORE AND OFFICE IN U.S<br />AND WORLDWIDE</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Two Column Section -->
    <section class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row g-0">
                <div class="col-md-6 bg-success text-center d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center p-4">
                    <img src="https://ui-themez.smartinnovates.net/items/swoo_html/inner_pages/assets/img/about/about2.png" alt="Delivery person" class="img-fluid" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 bg-tech p-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
                    <h2 class="h4 fw-bold mb-4">
                        We connect millions of buyers and sellers around the world, empowering people & creating economic
                        opportunity for all.
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                        Within our markets, millions of people around the world connect, both online and offline, to make, sell
                        and buy unique goods. We also offer a wide range of Seller Services and tools that help creative
                        entrepreneurs start, manage & scale their businesses.
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-success w-50 align-self-start">OUR SHOWREEL</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
